OL,3,CUK warns Britons in Middle East to
OL,4,Ctake shelter as Cobra meeting called
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has convened the
OL,7,Fgovernment's emergency Cobra committee
OL,8,Fas missile strikes escalate across the
OL,9,FMiddle East after US and Israeli
OL,10,Fforces attacked Iran on Saturday
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,FThe US and Israel described the
OL,14,Fattacks as a "pre-emptive" strike
OL,15,Fagainst a Tehran government intent on
OL,16,Fdeveloping nuclear weapons.
OL,18,FThe attacks across Iran prompted
OL,19,Fretaliation from Tehran, with missiles
OL,20,Freported to have targeted Israel and
OL,21,Fcountries across the Middle East.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@ZO]
