CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772409784
OL,3,CUK warns Britons in Middle East to
OL,4,Ctake shelter as Cobra meeting called
OL,6,FIt is understood that the UK was not
OL,7,Finvolved in the US-Israeli strikes.
OL,9,FA government spokesperson said the UK
OL,10,Fdid not want to see "further
OL,11,Fescalation into a wider regional
OL,12,Fconflict" and reiterated Britain's
OL,13,Fsupport for a negotiated solution to
OL,14,FIran's nuclear ambitions.
OL,16,FFollowing the strikes, the Foreign
OL,17,FOffice has warned against all travel
OL,18,Fto Israel while embassies in Bahrain,
OL,19,FQatar and the UAE have advised British
OL,20,Fnationals to shelter in place.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@IO]
