PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772409784
OL,3,CUK warns Britons in Middle East to
OL,4,Ctake shelter as Cobra meeting called
OL,6,FThe spokesperson added: "Iran must
OL,7,Fnever be allowed to develop a nuclear
OL,8,Fweapon and that is why we have
OL,9,Fcontinually supported efforts to reach
OL,10,Fa negotiated solution.
OL,12,F"Our immediate priority is the safety
OL,13,Fof UK nationals in the region and we
OL,14,Fwill provide them with consular
OL,15,Fassistance, available 24/7."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
